# Project Structure Rules

## Monorepo Layout
```
apps/
├── web/          # TanStack Start (frontend + BFF)
└── api/          # Hono (backend API)
packages/
├── shared/       # Zod schemas, types, utilities
├── ui/           # React component library
└── db/           # Prisma client + schema
tooling/
├── eslint/       # Shared ESLint config
├── typescript/   # Shared tsconfig bases
└── prettier/     # Shared Prettier config
specs/            # Feature specifications
adr/              # Architecture Decision Records
```

## Import Boundaries (Strict)
- `apps/` → can import from `packages/`
- `packages/` → can import from other `packages/` (no circular)
- `tooling/` → imported only by config files
- **Never**: `packages/` → `apps/` (dependency inversion violation)
- **Never**: circular imports between packages

## Package Naming
- Internal packages use `@repo/` scope: `@repo/shared`, `@repo/db`, `@repo/ui`
- Workspace protocol for internal deps: `"@repo/shared": "workspace:*"`

## File Organization Within Features
```
features/{name}/
├── {name}.route.ts        # Route definitions (API)
├── {name}.service.ts      # Business logic
├── {name}.schema.ts       # Zod schemas (or import from @repo/shared)
└── {name}.test.ts         # Colocated tests
```

## File Naming
- Files: `kebab-case.ts` or `{name}.{type}.ts`
- Types: `{name}.{type}.ts` where type is: `route`, `service`, `schema`, `test`
- Components: `PascalCase.tsx` or `kebab-case.tsx` (pick one, be consistent)
- Config files: standard names (`vite.config.ts`, `vitest.config.ts`, `tsconfig.json`)

## Barrel Exports
- Each package has `src/index.ts` that exports the public API
- Only export what consumers need — keep internals private
- Apps do NOT use barrel exports (tree-shaking handles it)

## Flat Over Nested
- Prefer flat directories — max 3 levels deep
- If a directory has only one file, it probably shouldn't be a directory
- Feature directories should be self-contained

## Configuration Hierarchy
- Root: `turbo.json`, `pnpm-workspace.yaml`, root `package.json`
- Per-package: `tsconfig.json` extends `../../tooling/typescript/base.json`
- Per-package: `vitest.config.ts` for test configuration
- Per-app: `vite.config.ts` for build configuration
